ion with a complex interaction term can be derived\nas the mean-field approximation of a Bose-Hubbard dimer with an additional\nLindblad term modelling two-particle losses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2013 16:51:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2013 21:58:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
