ents. Following this way it provides the possibility that\nthe pion DA will be determined by the global fit finally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 May 2013 13:17:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2013 12:34:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-12"}
